Naam Jaap Counter v2.9.1 — Background Temple Music

Upload/replace these files in the GitHub repository root:
1. index.html
2. config.js
3. sw.js
4. background-music.js
5. background-music.css
6. temple-music.mp3

Important:
- Upload all six files before testing, preferably in the same commit.
- Do not rename temple-music.mp3.
- Commit message: feat: add background temple music
- Wait 2–5 minutes for GitHub Pages.
- Open the app directly in Chrome, then use Ctrl+F5 or clear the PWA cache once.
- Open Settings → Background Temple Music → Start Music.
- Browser rules require one user tap before audio can play.

No Apps Script redeployment is required. This feature is frontend-only.
